x\to\infty
m,n
\left[(x^m + 1)^{1/n} - (x^m - 1)^{1/n}\right]x^{(mn-m)/n}
\left ( x^m + 1 \right )^{\frac{1}{n}} - \left (x^m - 1 \right)^{\frac{1}{n}} = x^{\frac{m}{n}} \left [ \left ( 1 + \frac{1}{x^m} \right )^{\frac{1}{n}} - \left (1 - \frac{1}{x^m} \right)^{\frac{1}{n}} \right ]
 \approx x^{\frac{m}{n}} \left [ \left ( 1 + \frac{1}{n x^m} \right ) - \left (1 - \frac{1}{n x^m} \right) \right ]
 = \frac{2 x^{\frac{m}{n}}}{n x^m} 
2/n
1+1+...+1=n
\lim_{x\to +\infty}\left[(x^m + 1)^{1/n} - (x^m - 1)^{1/n}\right]x^{(mn-m)/n} =\lim_{x\to +\infty}x^{\frac mn}\left[(1 + \frac1{x^m})^{1/n} - (1- \frac1{x^m})^{1/n}\right]x^{(mn-m)/n}= \lim_{x\to +\infty}\left[(1+ \frac1{x^m})^{1/n} - (1- \frac1{x^m})^{1/n}\right]x^{m} 
\alpha^{1/n}-\beta^{1/n}=\frac{\alpha-\beta^n}{\alpha^{{(n-1)}/n}+ \alpha^{{(n-2)}/n}\beta+...+\alpha\beta^{{(n-2)}/n}+\beta^{{(n-1)}/n}}
\lim_{x\to +\infty}\left[\frac{1+ \frac1{x^m}- 1+ \frac1{x^m}}{(1+ \frac1{x^m})^{{(n-1)}/n}+...+(1+ \frac1{x^m})^{{(n-1)}/n}}\right]x^m= \lim_{x\to +\infty}\left[\frac{2}{(1+ \frac1{x^m})^{{(n-1)}/n}+...+(1+ \frac1{x^m})^{{(n-1)}/n}}\right]
\lim_{x\to +\infty}\left[\frac2{(1+ \frac1{x^m})^{{(n-1)}/n}+...+(1+ \frac1{x^m})^{{(n-1)}/n}}\right]=\frac2n
